idence-03-defendant-a516424b54be.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Decodes plaintiff's PX-2 NOTAM code QFALC as an aerodrome-closure notice, relevant to whether the notice proves an airspace-region closure or only airport closures/permissions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T22:52:30Z\",\"sha256\":\"a516424b54be20e47eea237ca0ec110ca73d452356bfe11fca0f98f6a207fd9f\",\"size_bytes\":1095,\"source_description\":\"FAA Order 7930.2 appendix B page text, International NOTAM (Q) Codes, opened 2026-06-19. Relevant lines: Q-code groups use second/third letters for subject and fourth/fifth for status; FA means Aerodrome; LC means Closed.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.faa.gov/air_traffic/publications/atpubs/notam_html/appendix_b.html\",\"storage_name\":\"a5/a516424b54be20e47eea237ca0ec110ca73d452356bfe11fca0f98f6a207fd9f\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"FAA International NOTAM Q-code decode for QFALC\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T22:39:48Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_a6870de8ffed_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-a6870de8ffed\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-a6870de8ffed.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Primary-like NOTAM archive capture showing Iran OIIX A1010/26 effective 2026-05-22 20:46 UTC to 2026-05-25 08:30 UTC, closing airports in the west part of Tehran FIR with limited listed-airport exceptions and CAA permission requirement for civil IFR passenger flights.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T22:45:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"a6870de8ffed7d8cae93dd5e233bfbb041ccda9493c8db97496a0ffeead27054\",\"size_bytes\":1458,\"source_description\":\"Notamify page for OIIX NOTAM A1010/26, including raw NOTAM text and interpretation as captured in web search/open output.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/693f2d0f-54d3-433b-8128-49f5475ba269\",\"storage_name\":\"a6/a6870de8ffed7d8cae93dd5e233bfbb041ccda9493c8db97496a0ffeead27054\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Notamify capture of Iran NOTAM OIIX A1010/26\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T22:44:07Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_d767617fb81e_submitted-evidence-04-defendant-d767617fb81e\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-defendant-d767617fb81e.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Shows the ICAO/IATA mapping for the market-listed airports and the airports excepted in PX-2. This is relevant because PX-2's exception list includes only OISS/SYZ among the five market-listed airports, while plaintiff's secondary report says several listed airports remained operational.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T22:52:45Z\",\"sha256\":\"d767617fb81ee90a4fac9440332aab2a0bf11de9a2536205cd0d0a7ede759714\",\"size_bytes\":4129,\"source_description\":\"OurAirports Iran airports CSV retrieved with curl and filtered for the five market-listed airports plus the eight airport identifiers excepted in PX-2 NOTAM A1010/26.\",\"source_url\":\"https://ourairports.com/countries/IR/airports.csv\",\"storage_name\":\"d7/d767617fb81ee90a4fac9440332aab2a0bf11de9a2536205cd0d0a7ede759714\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"OurAirports Iran airport code extract for market-listed and NOTAM-excepted airports\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T22:32:39Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_e61df84283cc_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"market-page.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"e61df84283cc858bfd0cf8235c6f1d53a10d6e1c37b2d97256da8f1e6391cc17\",\"size_bytes\":4971,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"e6/e61df84283cc858bfd0cf8235c6f1d53a10d6e