t part of Tehran FIR with limited listed-airport exceptions and CAA permission requirement for civil IFR passenger flights.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T22:45:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"a6870de8ffed7d8cae93dd5e233bfbb041ccda9493c8db97496a0ffeead27054\",\"size_bytes\":1458,\"source_description\":\"Notamify page for OIIX NOTAM A1010/26, including raw NOTAM text and interpretation as captured in web search/open output.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/693f2d0f-54d3-433b-8128-49f5475ba269\",\"storage_name\":\"a6/a6870de8ffed7d8cae93dd5e233bfbb041ccda9493c8db97496a0ffeead27054\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Notamify capture of Iran NOTAM OIIX A1010/26\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T22:44:07Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_d767617fb81e_submitted-evidence-04-defendant-d767617fb81e\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-defendant-d767617fb81e.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Shows the ICAO/IATA mapping for the market-listed airports and the airports excepted in PX-2. This is relevant because PX-2's exception list includes only OISS/SYZ among the five market-listed airports, while plaintiff's secondary report says several listed airports remained operational.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T22:52:45Z\",\"sha256\":\"d767617fb81ee90a4fac9440332aab2a0bf11de9a2536205cd0d0a7ede759714\",\"size_bytes\":4129,\"source_description\":\"OurAirports Iran airports CSV retrieved with curl and filtered for the five market-listed airports plus the eight airport identifiers excepted in PX-2 NOTAM A1010/26.\",\"source_url\":\"https://ourairports.com/countries/IR/airports.csv\",\"storage_name\":\"d7/d767617fb81ee90a4fac9440332aab2a0bf11de9a2536205cd0d0a7ede759714\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"OurAirports Iran airport code extract for market-listed and NOTAM-excepted airports\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T22:32:39Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_e61df84283cc_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"market-page.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"e61df84283cc858bfd0cf8235c6f1d53a10d6e1c37b2d97256da8f1e6391cc17\",\"size_bytes\":4971,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"e6/e61df84283cc858bfd0cf8235c6f1d53a10d6e1c37b2d97256da8f1e6391cc17\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"market-page.txt\"}]},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-19T23:16:46.316832875Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C10\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C10\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":879222,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":18}}"}],"details":{"mode":"call","mcpResult":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C10\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260619223222\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C10\nremaining_ms: 879222\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260619223222\",\"member_id\":\"C10\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T22:40:32Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_16946d327688_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-16946d327688\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-16946d327688.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Credible secondary reporting corroborating the NOTAM source, Iran Civil Aviation Authority issuance, May 22-May 25 window, eight-airport exception list including listed market airports, daylight-only restrictions, fresh CAA approval requirement, and commercial rerouting.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T22:46:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"16946d327688bbaa8